<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Marta) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル？
口の周りについてるの、なに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil? What's that around your mouth?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？
ああ、ケチャップだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh?
Oh, it's ketchup.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>さっきまで、ファラさんのところで
手料理をごちそうになってたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Farah-san treated me to a homecooked
meal at her place earlier.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>えぇぇぇぇぇ！！！？
なにそれ、私聞いてないよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whaaaaaat?!!!
What the heck? I wasn't informed about this!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……許せない。
私だけのエミルを
手料理を武器に誘惑するなんて！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Unforgiveable. How dare she try to
seduce MY Emil and mine alone, and
with a homecooked meal as her weapon!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？　マ、マルタ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Ma-Marta?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>戦争よ！！
これは女の戦争なんだから！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is war!!
What she's done amounts to a woman's war!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
